{"tid":2317052,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"北區好鄰舍：毒品調查科跟進！！","createTime":"2020-12-08T09:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T10:49:36.000Z","uid":262445,"like":11,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"38b8bc883cefbaecfdae01f206df21d512379162","tid":2317052,"uid":262445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AARJW2n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAARJW2n.png&h=ee47a07b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日下午兩時半，十位隸屬毒品調查科&mdash;財富調查組的警員手持搜查令到本會觀塘聚會點，要求聯絡本會堂主任及公司董事以帶返警署協助調查。警方現正搜查物品，預備帶走部份信件。<br />\n未確定警方接下來會否到粉嶺聚會點進行搜查。<br />\n<br />\n請為教會禱告。<br />\n<br />\nAround 1430 today, 10 police officers from Financial Investigation, Narcotics Bureau reached our gathering point at Kwun Tong with a search warrant, and they are now carrying out investigation at our entity and prepare to obtain documents, at the same time requesting contact of church pastor and directors of the church company to assist the investigation.<br />\nIt is not yet confirmed whether they will conduct further investigation at our Fanling church shortly.<br />\n<br />\nPlease pray for us.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屈教會藏毒....<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1561265357501167/posts/2456033231357704/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1561265357501167%2Fposts%2F2456033231357704%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3WwEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=c4f330ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1561265357501167/posts/2456033231357704/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"43abfbd45a7fadc2694301506be359616e8812a3","tid":2317052,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:41:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ff63e27138762ab